desc: Vechter bikes is Melbourne's premier fixed gear online store, specialising in track bike frames, fixed-gear, single speed parts and components. We stock brands such as FTWCRW, SRAM, H + Son, Cult, Burgh, IZUMI, SAPIM and more. One stop shop for custom fixed gear bikes perfect straight from the velodrom to the street.
